<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Portal de Notícias</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <div class="topo">
        <h1>G1</h1>
    </div>

    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li>Brasil</li>
            <li>Mundo</li>
            <li>Economia</li>
            <li>Tecnologia</li>
            <li>Esportes</li>
            <li>Entretenimento</li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
</header>

<main>

<section class="principal">

<div class="noticia-grande">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x400">
<h2>Grande notícia do dia que chama muita atenção</h2>
<p>Resumo da notícia principal do portal.</p>
</div>

<div class="noticias-laterais">

<div class="noticia">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x200">
<h3>Notícia importante</h3>
</div>

<div class="noticia">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x200">
<h3>Outra notícia relevante</h3>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="grid-noticias">

<div class="card">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x150">
<h4>Notícia 1</h4>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x150">
<h4>Notícia 2</h4>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x150">
<h4>Notícia 3</h4>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x150">
<h4>Notícia 4</h4>
</div>

</section>

</main>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 Portal de Notícias</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
